Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2E3799&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Nanbara had completed blueprints for GOD's\NRS Device, which can convert any matter into energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanbara escaped GOD and tore the blueprints\Ninto nine pieces to entrust to his old colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD has stolen one of the pieces,\Nand the X Rider holds three.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus does a deadly race for the\Nremaining five pieces begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!\NX Rider's Great Transformation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18\i1}Oki Institute of Biology{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief! That makes thirteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, GOD's gonna kill\Nevery scientist in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief... Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a portrait of Napoleon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. The same one was found\Nat the scene of all these crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that begs the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\i1}Nonaka Youichirou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko, wake up! It's a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A burglar...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Weird. There's no one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Just you two'!? Is this any\Nway to treat your guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! You shouldn't be playing pranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell us you're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we heard a strange noise, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, there really is someone else in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoes are wet! Something's seriously wrong!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Dr. Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,M-my husband's in America! Wh-who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My deepest apologies, madam. You may address\Nme as Spider Napoleon, of GOD's Villain Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, madam... Won't you give\Nme the blueprint sent to Dr. Nonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, I am a gentleman. I\Ncould never raise a hand to a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try one, madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My cute little babies just love beautiful\Nladies! He seems attached to you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my mom go! I've got the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-The boy!\N-Itaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! I have it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alright now. The\Nchief told me you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Jin Keisuke? I've\Nbeen looking forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is mine! The word\N'impossible' means nothing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I shall settle for this blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, where'd he go?\NI can't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all your weak spots!\NTry my Vampire Spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Within minutes, you'll\Nbe a desiccated corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something the matter, X Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast... What's happening\Nto me...? I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you figured it out, X Rider?\NMy web drained all of your energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Rider Kick's useless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiderweb Jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle, struggle! The more you\Nstruggle, the more energy you waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No use... Strength... fading...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Die!\N-Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know who I am? That says\Nmore about you than it does me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me... Kamen Rider V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider V3, eh? Alright,\NI'll kill you too! En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-where did you go, V3?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Just wanted to draw me out,\Ndid you? Show yourself, V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Spider Napoleon. I don't have\Ntime to fight you now. We'll do this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, V3!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to operate on Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that can stop Spider\NNapoleon is... Mercury Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.10,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mercury Power...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!! That blueprint was a counterfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tricked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my mom go! I've got the blueprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat! He really did have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mercury Power will allow X to perform\Nthe Vacuum Hell Wheel technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can only be used with\Na Mercury Circuit installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, it requires a\Ntransfusion of all one's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you every drop\Nof my blood if I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirou, big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's got Itaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Itaru was hiding the real\Nblueprint all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-I thought they already took it?\N-No, that was a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake? But... I have to stay\Nhere until the operation's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Shirou, look after Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well, let's see how\Nthey like a Spiderweb Jungle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, gents!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of time... If I don't\Ninstall the Mercury Circuit now--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak! Where have you\Nhidden the blueprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'll tell you! I promised\Nmy dad I'd keep it a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see... Then I'll\Nhave to ask less politely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... Now all he needs is\Na shock to bring him out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the times!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel like talking now, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Mom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, are you ok? Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast you, GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait, I'll tell you!\N-No! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-The blueprint is--\N-You can't tell them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in Itaru's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform... V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-V3!\N-Get Itaru out of here!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you owe me\Na match, V3! En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! Spiderweb Jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like that, V3?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't move, can you? You made\Nthe same mistake as the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke? You're alive!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take more than that to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the same man any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Spider Napoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vampire Spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, d-don't tell me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get me with that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the Spiderweb Jungle!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How does the Vacuum Hell Wheel work?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This special move uses an\Nenemy's power against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,First, it reduces their offensive power by rolling them\Nalong at high speed, driving their head into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, they're thrown into the air and fall back to earth with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, an X Kick clinches the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazami, the Mercury Power worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't say? Good work, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With the fourth blueprint piece as\Ngood as yours, you can afford a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.40,0:23:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke has been powered\Nup by Kazami Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten stronger, X!\NNow crush King Dark's ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(40,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark and the X Rider continue their\Ndeadly race for the mysterious RS Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD sets their sights on a blueprint piece hidden in a young ballerina's pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"Mortal Combat!! X Rider Versus X Rider!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.82,0:23:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
